[Note:
This page contains further work on Propostion 12 from Viète's Effectionum geometricarum canonica recensio (1593). At the end, Harriot makes the same observation as on Add MS 6785, f. 94, that the method of solving the equation is essentially the same as the 'ancient' method, that is, the traditional numerical method taught in every algebra text.
]

