[Note:
This sheet refers to Stevin's L 19arithmétique ... aussi l 19algebre (1585), page 214. On that page, Stevin wrote: 'Et multipliant √bino. 1 + √2, par √bino. 3 + √5, le produict sera √quadrino. √3 + √6 + √5 + √10.' Harriot has re-written the same calculation in his own notation: [2]1+2, and so on.
